{"tid":879111,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"富士山顛倒放！坂茂打造日本富士山世界遺產中心","createTime":"2018-10-27T16:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T16:14:42.000Z","uid":74778,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b3387e78b8cc5a98887743f69e8e722d077f213","tid":879111,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:14:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 富士山顛倒放！坂茂打造日本富士山世界遺產中心</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/180127-6_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F180127-6_01.jpg&h=89e64e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提及日本的文化象徵指標，富士山無疑是最好的人選，富士山不只是山，他所代表的更是一座信仰中心、創作者的靈感源頭，多少的日本歷史、藝術及文化樣貌都因他而生。而在 2013 年富士山終於被聯合國教科文組織（UNESCO）列為世界文化遺產之一，雖然有些意外這個身分來的比想像中的慢，但無論如何他對日本文化所帶來的影響也終於得到肯定，當時靜岡縣為了振興當地旅遊業，便在 2014 年舉辦了世界遺產中心的設計方案競賽，藉此宣揚富士山的歷史與自然風貌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/001212_1cf7814bcd764bef1617dfd415e79caa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F001212_1cf7814bcd764bef1617dfd415e79caa.png&h=ca3e0d39&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/001213_9919e1913ca2e92985ecab5d1ab604db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F001213_9919e1913ca2e92985ecab5d1ab604db.png&h=9f7f9032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 238 件的設計草案中，由日本知名建築設計師坂茂的作品雀屏中選，當時眾多的設計提案幾乎所都提出了模仿富士山作為屋頂的想法，但唯有坂茂的設計背道而馳，以「逆富士」為概念脫穎而出。如今，外型特殊的富士山世界遺產中心也已經在 2017 年底正式開幕，引來世界各地旅客朝聖。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/001237_106e73775869d7b26d4250746bacea6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F001237_106e73775869d7b26d4250746bacea6e.png&h=37b1fc74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/001239_53c38cac7adacf1bde6dd2a112bf9d3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F001239_53c38cac7adacf1bde6dd2a112bf9d3f.png&h=c31381d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這座全新的世界遺產中心，使用日本在地檜木交織打造格狀錐體倒立在地面上，而山的全貌則可以透過周圍水面映造出來。建築主體被玻璃分為室內、室外兩個區域，走進建築內，拜訪者可以從地面爬上五樓頂層，在懸空的步道上瞻仰遠方真正的富士山身影，其他也包含了一個小型影像廳和用來展示富士山影像資料的迴廊，讓拜訪者可以透過不同面向，進一步認識富士山之美。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/180127-6_06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F180127-6_06.jpg&h=8323478d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/180127-6_07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F180127-6_07.jpg&h=4f894713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/180127-6_08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F180127-6_08.jpg&h=96a955bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/001359_cc86b7d96ea412f2586afd64c5f64799.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F001359_cc86b7d96ea412f2586afd64c5f64799.png&h=74f38b6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/001401_340fa1ef6fabda9923785f74aaef976d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F001401_340fa1ef6fabda9923785f74aaef976d.png&h=84221dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/001403_942fc6cd79c3bcedb393a19ccdc04e21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F001403_942fc6cd79c3bcedb393a19ccdc04e21.png&h=7a74aa96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n靜岡縣富士山世界遺產中心<br />\n地址｜ 静岡県富士宮市宮町 5-12<br />\n開館時間｜9：00 &ndash; 17：00，閉館前 30 分鐘為最後入館時間<br />\n休館日｜每月第三個星期二（如遇到節日，則為隔日休館）<br />\n門票｜成人為每人 300 日元（團體票200 日元）、15 歲以下及 70 歲以上免費入場、學生免費入場、身障者及其照顧者免費入場<br />\n <br />\nSource from 静岡県富士山世界遺産センター, 坂茂建築設計<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.designwant.com/r2568.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fr2568.html&d=OwLvdmaINEXasGCo93XTIsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=30e4962d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.designwant.com/r2568.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}